> The sunflare's not working properly in 1.3.1, its the thing where both the stock and scatterer sunflares are overlapping. I assume this'll be fixed soon
> 

They do work. The issue is now Scatterer, it’s how KSP implements their stock sun flare. You can fix it using kopernicus and creating a confit with this in it: 

    @Kopernicus:NEEDS[scatterer]
    {	   @Body:HAS[@Template:HAS[#name[Sun]]]{	%ScaledVersion	{		%Light		{			%sunLensFlareColor = 0,0,0,0		}	}
        	}
    }
